**Query #5**
--Which company has the highest revenue in the Technology industry? And what is that max revenue?
    SELECT company_name, MAX(revenue)
    FROM fortune_companies
    WHERE industry='Technology';

| company_name | MAX(revenue) |
| ------------ | ------------ |
| Company F    | 420.1        |

